    <summary>Provides arguments for cloning or customizing a typeface with specific variation settings.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`SKFontArguments` provides arguments for cloning or customizing a typeface with specific variation settings, palette choices, and palette color overrides. Pass an instance to <see cref="M:SkiaSharp.SKTypeface.Clone(SkiaSharp.SKFontArguments)" /> to create a derived typeface.

## Examples

```csharp
var args = new SKFontArguments
{
    CollectionIndex = 0,
    PaletteIndex = 1
};
using var typeface = originalTypeface.Clone(args);
```
]]></format></remarks>
  </Docs>
